{"tid":2417552,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日終於鼓起勇氣同鍾意嘅女仔講野","createTime":"2021-02-22T03:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T12:09:10.000Z","uid":359455,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e086630cc88ca1b34c4001371e9e0f8882b9b51","tid":2417552,"uid":359455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"各位觀眾大家好！！！今個po會同大家分享我嘅感情事<br />\n我有去開機鋪打機嘅習慣，大約每星期一次，有次就見到個長頭髮嘅女仔，雖然戴左口罩不過我都覺得佢係靚女，所以第一次見到就已經鍾意左佢，因為覺得佢好靚，不過我份人就好細膽嘅，加上佢就有朋友在場，所以見左幾次都冇挑佢機。<br />\n<br />\n直到尋日，我又喺機鋪見到姖，佢著左條超正嘅短裙，令我更鍾意佢了，所以我就鼓起勇氣同佢挑機，結果佢都同左我打機。可能係我太專注個比賽，所以冇乜心跳加速嘅感覺，最後我都冇同佢示愛同拎電話，我真係好失敗呀，同埋我同佢都係差唔多高，佢會唔會嫌棄我呢？😂"},{"pid":"6781782cfb48e63de56214941d341016a93d3eb0","tid":2417552,"uid":265217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"樓主幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed60d8a55aeb94e0b534b4ec15bb9069709f3381","tid":2417552,"uid":359455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6781782cfb48e63de56214941d341016a93d3eb0","tid":2417552,"uid":265217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"樓主幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"18-22"},{"pid":"bb56e1adf4bb0f39a5348c6797b637f0ae1bb330","tid":2417552,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:54:17.000Z","msg":"Kenny哥幾時開返個埃豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bf8b9e49d013e2f84171195ae534e2d40adec8","tid":2417552,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:03:16.000Z","msg":"😂😂😂😂😂😂"},{"pid":"957095ed3818cf1fb396283c24d10ac9d5b44f3b","tid":2417552,"uid":363208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:16:56.000Z","msg":"Kenny哥你之前ig dm過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670698a7fecb211d